# derived/archive_review_queue/.gitkeep
# Archive Builder ambiguity review queue.
# Files written here require user review before ingestion.
# Contents:
#   <RUN_ID>__ambiguous_files.csv       — files that failed archive_classifier checks
#   <RUN_ID>__ambiguous_precinct_ids.csv — precinct IDs that could not be safely joined
#   <RUN_ID>__low_confidence_fingerprints.csv — files with fingerprint_conf < 0.85
